<ITEM> A di&s;ordered &s;tate like &s;leep.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Conge&s;tion.</LABEL>
<ITEM> A collection of humours.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Contu&s;ion.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Pre&s;&s;ure, &s;queeze, cru&s;h.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Con&s;tricted.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Drawn together, bound.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Debility.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Feeblene&s;s, weakne&s;s.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Decoction.</LABEL>
<ITEM> That which is made by boiling.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Delirium.</LABEL>
