<LABEL>E<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ctution.</LABEL>
<ITEM> A belching.</ITEM>
<LABEL>F<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ices.</LABEL>
<ITEM> The po&s;terior cavity of the mouth.</ITEM>
<PB N="98" REF="029891_0097_0FE2C6071C08AE78">
<LABEL>Flaccid.</LABEL>
<ITEM>Relaxed, loo&s;e.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Ge&s;tation.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Pa&s;&s;ive exerci&s;e, as riding.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Grumous.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Clodded.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Intermittent.</LABEL>
<ITEM> With an interval.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Laceratiou.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Tare, rend.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Mucilaginous.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Jelly-like, &s;limy, vi&s;cous.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Narcotic.</LABEL>
<ITEM> That which de&s;troys &s;en&s;e and &s;tupifies.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Nau&s;ea.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Sickne&s;s at the &s;tomach.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Obe&s;ity.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Fatne&s;s.</ITEM>
