<LABEL>Pu&s;tules.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Pimples with matter in them.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Radically.</LABEL>
<ITEM> From the root, the bottom.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Remit.</LABEL>
<ITEM> To le&s;&s;en, or cea&s;e partially.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Re&s;piration.</LABEL>
<ITEM> The act of breathing.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Sedate.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Given to inactivity, quiet.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Sloughs.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Mortified &s;pots.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Spheroidal.</LABEL>
<ITEM> Like a &s;phere.</ITEM>
